<i>noun</i>: 참상 [참상], 참사 [참사], 참변 [참변], 참극 [참극], 비극 [비ː극] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참상 [참상]</dt><br>
<dd>disaster; tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>끔찍하고 비참한 모습이나 상황.</dd><br>
<dd>A tragic, awful scene or situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참사 [참사]</dt><br>
<dd>disaster; tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>비참하고 끔찍한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A tragic, awful occurrence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참변 [참변]</dt><br>
<dd>disaster; tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 일어나는 끔찍하고 비참한 재앙이나 사고.</dd><br>
<dd>An awful, tragic catastrophe or accident that happens suddenly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참극 [참극]</dt><br>
<dd>tragedy; disaster; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 슬프고 끔찍한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A sad and awful occurrence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비극 [비ː극]</dt><br>
<dd>1. tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>매우 슬프고 비참한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A very sad and miserable thing.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>슬프거나 비참한 결말로 끝나는 극.</dd><br>
<dd>A piece of theater that has a sad or miserable ending.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>